{"tid":2426193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：憂慮疫情有上升趨勢，防控工作在有必要時加強，呼籲市民保持警惕及不要群組聚集","createTime":"2021-02-28T01:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T02:47:13.000Z","uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"867b78ed940b6678e80e06ad9a10aec1fdff5bdc","tid":2426193,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗憂慮疫情仍然反覆，甚至有上升趨勢，強調政府的防控工作必須持續，及在有必要時加強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425582&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3hckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e7123bd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425582&h=c7e8bff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425582</a>"},{"pid":"5ec5f8d55f74a715e1d50a7e05a4022899995551","tid":2426193,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"張建宗在網誌中指，近日出現餐廳群組感染個案外，社區持續存在源頭不明的個案，呼籲市民保持警惕，盡量不要群組聚集，而政府的防控工作必須持續及在有必要時加強。"},{"pid":"3c1129bdc6d3ed6650db298c5764a2a67d0d6ce3","tid":2426193,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"安心出殯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ea7777e687fdc40f3c7af2b3f7c021c856554b","tid":2426193,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DC5ymyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDC5ymyw.png&h=a71876ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時繁殖率已升至1.295 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.g